/* ====================================================================================================================
 * BASE STYLES
 * ====================================================================================================================*/
.flexslider {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.flexslider .slides &gt; li {
  display: none;
  -webkit-backface-visibility: hidden;
}

.flexslider .slides img {
  width: 100%;
  display: block;
}

.flexslider .slides:after {
  content: "\0020";
  display: block;
  clear: both;
  visibility: hidden;
  line-height: 0;
  height: 0;
}

html[xmlns] .flexslider .slides {
  display: block;
}

* html .flexslider .slides {
  height: 1%;
}

.no-js .flexslider .slides &gt; li:first-child {
  display: block;
}

/* ====================================================================================================================
 * DEFAULT THEME
 * ====================================================================================================================*/
.flexslider {
  margin: 0 0 60px;
  background: #fff;
  border: 0;
  position: relative;
  zoom: 1;
  -webkit-border-radius: 4px;
  -moz-border-radius: 4px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  -webkit-box-shadow: "" 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  -moz-box-shadow: "" 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  -o-box-shadow: "" 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  box-shadow: "" 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.flexslider .slides {
  zoom: 1;
}

.flexslider .slides img {
  height: auto;
  -moz-user-select: none;
}

.flex-viewport {
  max-height: 2000px;
  -webkit-transition: all 1s ease;
  -moz-transition: all 1s ease;
  -ms-transition: all 1s ease;
  -o-transition: all 1s ease;
  transition: all 1s ease;
  margin-left: -1px;
}

.loading .flex-viewport {
  max-height: 300px;
}

.carousel li {
  margin-right: 5px;
}

.flex-direction-nav {
  /**height: 0;*/
  display: none;
}

.flexslider:hover .flex-direction-nav .flex-prev {
  opacity: 0.7;
  left: 10px;
}

.flexslider:hover .flex-direction-nav .flex-prev:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

.flexslider:hover .flex-direction-nav .flex-next {
  opacity: 0.7;
  right: 10px;
}

.flexslider:hover .flex-direction-nav .flex-next:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

.flex-direction-nav .flex-disabled {
  opacity: 0 !important;
  filter: alpha(opacity=0);
  cursor: default;
  z-index: -1;
}

.flex-pauseplay a {
  display: block;
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 5px;
  left: 10px;
  opacity: 0.8;
  z-index: 10;
  overflow: hidden;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: #000;
}

.flex-pauseplay a:before {
  font-family: "flexslider-icon";
  font-size: 20px;
  display: inline-block;
  content: '\f004';
}

.flex-pauseplay a:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

.flex-pauseplay a.flex-play:before {
  content: '\f003';
}

.flex-control-nav {
  width: 100%;
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -40px;
  text-align: center;
}

.flex-control-nav li {
  margin: 0 6px;
  display: inline-block;
  zoom: 1;
  *display: inline;
}

.flex-control-paging li a {
  width: 11px;
  height: 11px;
  display: block;
  background: #666;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  cursor: pointer;
  text-indent: -9999px;
  -webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  -moz-box-shadow: inset 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  -o-box-shadow: inset 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  -webkit-border-radius: 20px;
  -moz-border-radius: 20px;
  border-radius: 20px;
}

.flex-control-paging li a:hover {
  background: #333;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
}

.flex-control-paging li a.flex-active {
  background: #000;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  cursor: default;
}

.flex-control-thumbs {
  margin: 5px 0 0;
  position: static;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.flex-control-thumbs li {
  width: 25%;
  float: left;
  margin: 0;
}

.flex-control-thumbs img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  opacity: .7;
  cursor: pointer;
  -moz-user-select: none;
  -webkit-transition: all 1s ease;
  -moz-transition: all 1s ease;
  -ms-transition: all 1s ease;
  -o-transition: all 1s ease;
  transition: all 1s ease;
}

.flex-control-thumbs img:hover {
  opacity: 1;
}

.flex-control-thumbs .flex-active {
  opacity: 1;
  cursor: default;
}

/* REQUIRED CSS: change your reflow breakpoint here (35em below) */
@media (max-width: 35em) {
  /* uncomment out the line below if you don't want the sortable headers to show */
  /* table.ui-table-reflow thead { display: none; } */
  /* css for reflow &amp; reflow2 widgets */
  .ui-table-reflow td,
  .ui-table-reflow th {
    -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
    -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    float: right;
    /* if not using the stickyHeaders widget (not the css3 version)
     * the "!important" flag, and "height: auto" can be removed */
    width: 100% !important;
    height: auto !important;
  }

  /* reflow widget only */
  .ui-table-reflow tbody td[data-title]:before {
    color: #469;
    font-size: .9em;
    content: attr(data-title);
    float: left;
    width: 50%;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    text-align: bottom;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* reflow2 widget only */
  table.ui-table-reflow .ui-table-cell-label.ui-table-cell-label-top {
    display: block;
    padding: .4em 0;
    margin: .4em 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: .9em;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  table.ui-table-reflow .ui-table-cell-label {
    padding: .4em;
    min-width: 30%;
    display: inline-block;
    margin: -.4em 1em -.4em -.4em;
  }
}
/* end media query */
/* reflow2 widget */
.ui-table-reflow .ui-table-cell-label {
  display: none;
}

  .ate-body thead tr {
    position: absolute;
    top: -9999px;
    left: -9999px;
  }
  .ate-body tr {
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }
  .ate-body tr:nth-child(odd) {
    background: #ccc;
  }
  .ate-body td {
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 50%;
  }
  .ate-body td:before {
    /* Now like a table header */
    position: absolute;
    /* Top/left values mimic padding */
    top: 5px;
    left: 6px;
    width: 45%;
    padding-right: 10px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(1):before {
    content: attr(data-name);
  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(2):before {
    content: attr(data-name);
  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(3):before {
    content: attr(data-name);

  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(5):before {

  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(6):before {

  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(7):before {
    content: attr(data-name);
  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(8):before {
    content: attr(data-name);
  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(9):before {
    content: attr(data-name);
  }
  .ate-body td:nth-of-type(10):before {
    content: attr(data-name);
  }
}

.mobile-nav__icon--menu {
  /*@include svg-background(hamburger);*/
  background-image: url("/sites/es/images/home_page/mobile_menu.png");
}

.mobile-nav__icon--search {
  /*@include svg-background(search-white);*/
  background-image: url("/sites/es/images/home_page/btn_search_blue.png");
  position: relative;
  top: -1px;
  width: 20px;
}

.mobile-nav__links {
  background-color: white;
  background-color: white;
  color: #111111;
  padding: 0;
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  z-index: 110;
}

.nav--mobile {
  border-bottom: 1px solid #333333;
  border-top: 1px solid #333333;
  margin: 0;
}
.nav--mobile .nav {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}
.nav--mobile .nav__item {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}
.nav--mobile .nav__item + .nav__item {
  border-top: 1px solid #333333;
}
.nav--mobile .nav__link {
  background-color: transparent;
  background-image: none;
  border: 0;
  -webkit-border-radius: 0;
  -moz-border-radius: 0;
  -ms-border-radius: 0;
  -o-border-radius: 0;
  border-radius: 0;
  -webkit-box-shadow: none;
  -moz-box-shadow: none;
  box-shadow: none;
  color: #111111;
  display: block;
  font-family: "Roboto", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: bold;
  line-height: 1.25;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 1em 1em;
  text-align: left;
  text-decoration: none;
  text-shadow: none;
  white-space: normal;
  width: 100%;
}
.nav--mobile .nav__link:focus, .nav--mobile .nav__link:hover, .nav--mobile .nav__link:active, .nav--mobile .nav__link.is-active {
  background-color: #777777;
  color: white;
  outline: 0;
}
.nav--mobile .nav__link--parent:after {
  /*@include svg-background(chevron-right-cyan);*/
  background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,");
  background-position: 0 50%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  content: '';
  display: inline-block;
  height: 20px;
  margin-left: 1em;
  vertical-align: top;
  width: 20px;
}
[dir="rtl"] .nav--mobile .nav__link--parent:after {
  /*@include svg-background(chevron-left-cyan);*/
  background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,");
  margin-left: 0;
  margin-right: 1em;
}
.nav--mobile .nav__link--parent.is-active:after {
  /*@include svg-background(chevron-down-cyan);*/
  background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,");
}
.nav--mobile .nav__link--parent .caret {
  display: none;
}
.nav--mobile .nav--subnav {
  display: none;
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}
.nav--mobile .nav--subnav .nav__item {
  background: #eeeeee;
}
.nav--mobile .nav--subnav .nav__item + .nav__item {
  border-top: 1px solid #cccccc;
}
.nav--mobile .nav--subnav .nav__link {
  color: #333333;
  padding-left: 1.5em;
}
.nav--mobile .nav--subnav .nav__link:focus, .nav--mobile .nav--subnav .nav__link:hover, .nav--mobile .nav--subnav .nav__link:active {
  background-color: #dddddd;
}

.block--pane-homepage-header-links {
  display: none;
  right: 235px;
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
}
@media (min-width: 700px) {
  .block--pane-homepage-header-links {
    display: block;
  }
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-links .block__title {
  display: none;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav li, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav .open {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0 0 0 1.5em;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav li a, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav .open a {
  display: block;
  font-family: "Roboto", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  letter-spacing: 0;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 44px;
  padding: 0;
  color: #157cbd;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 1em;
  background: transparent;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav li a:hover, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav li a:active, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav li a:focus, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav .open a:hover, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav .open a:active, .block--pane-homepage-header-links ul.nav .open a:focus {
  background: transparent;
}

.block--pane-homepage-header-search-box {
  display: none;
  position: absolute;
  right: 5px;
  top: 10px;
}
@media (min-width: 700px) {
  .block--pane-homepage-header-search-box {
    display: block;
  }
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-search-box .block__title {
  display: none;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-search-box .content form {
  border: 2px solid #CBCBCB;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-search-box .content form input {
  vertical-align: middle;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-search-box .content form input.searchBox {
  border-right: 0;
  display: block;
  float: left;
  font-family: "Roboto", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  height: 20px;
  padding: 4px;
  color: #333;
  width: 165px;
  right: 0;
  border: 0;
}
.block--pane-homepage-header-search-box .content form input#search_submit {
  border: 0;
  display: block;
  float: left;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  height: 25px;
  background-color: transparent;
}

@media (min-width: 700px) {
  #footer {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }
}
#footer .logo {
  top: 3px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  #footer .logo {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
}
#footer ul, #footer li {
  list-style: none;
}
#footer li, #footer span {
  color: #fff;
  font-family: "Roboto", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
}
@media (min-width: 700px) {
  #footer .block {
    float: left;
    width: 25%;
  }
}
#footer .block .block__title {
  display: none;
}
#footer .footer-column {
  line-height: 1.3;
}
@media (min-width: 576px) and (max-width: 814px) {
  #footer .footer-column {
    padding-left: 0;
    /*width: 27%;*/
  }
}
@media (max-width: 814px) {
  #footer .footer-column {
    text-align: left;
    display: block;
  }
}
#footer .footer-column ul {
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-left: 0;
  padding-left: 0;
}
@media (min-width: 767px) {
  #footer .footer-column ul {
    position: relative;
    top: -5px;
  }
}
#footer .footer-column ul li a {
  font-size: 1.33333em;
  color: #000;
}
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  #footer .footer-column ul li a {
    padding-left: 5px;
  }
}
#footer .footer-column ul li a:hover, #footer .footer-column ul li a:focus {
  text-decoration: underline;
}
#footer .footer-column.footer-column-1 {
  position: relative;
  left: 45px;
}
@media (max-width: 815px) {
  #footer .footer-column.footer-column-1 {
    left: 0;
  }
}
#footer .seal-icons {
  text-align: right;
  padding-right: 0;
}
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  #footer .seal-icons {
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
}
#footer .seal-icons img {
  margin: 0 15px;
  width: 100px;
}
@media (min-width: 576px) and (max-width: 814px) {
  #footer .seal-icons img {
    width: 40%;
  }
}
#footer .seal-icons img:last-of-type {
  margin-right: 0;
}
